source: Alright. That one's the last time.
target: Oso ongi. Hau da azken aldia.

source: As stubborn as our elder masters.
Came to the wrong place, pal.
Can't you see there's no place for you here?
target: Ez al zara ohartu hemen ez dagoela zuretzako lekurik?
Argi dago ez zarela nahikoa azkarra.

source: Come on, keep up with me.
Come on, show me what you got.
Come on, try and hit me.
Come on, try and hit me.
Come on. Try harder, you fool!
Come out and face me, coward!
target: Zatoz eta egidazu aurre, kakati hori!

source: Come over here. There's space for us to fight.

target: Kaka zaharra... akabatu ninduela uste nuen.

source: Did you forget how to fight?
Do not play games with me.
Do not play these kinds of games with me.
target: Ez zaitez nirekin horrelako jolastean aritu.

source: Do you ever plan on hitting me?
target: Ni noizbait jotzeko planik ba al duzu?

source: Don't bother trying that on me.

target: Ez eman pausu bat ere gehiago!

source: Don't insult me by trying to spare me.
target: Ez nazazu iraindu errukia erakusten saiatuz.

source: Don't insult me with that move.
Don't worry, you'll feel better afterward.
target: Ez arduratu, gero hobeki sentituko zara.

source: Enjoying the bitter taste of death?
Fine, let's see how you handle my Pak Mei.
target: Ederki, ea nola daramazun nire Pak Mei-a.

source: First time I've seen you here.
Fuck you doin' in here, pal?
Get out here and face me!
Gonna pop your head like a zit.
Hey! How'd you get in here?
Hey, this is a private party, fool.
target: Aizu, hau festa pribatua da, baboa.

source: How can you get up after that?
How did you survive my blades?
I bet Sifu didn't teach you this one!
target: Ziur Sifuk ez zizula hau irakatsi!

source: I bet your dead father didn't think to teach you this.
target: Ziur zure hildako aitak ez zizula hau irakatsi!

source: I can do this all day.
I can relieve you of your pain.
I can see your body giving up on you.
target: Zure gorputza amore ematen hasi dela ikusten dut.

source: I can wait all day long for you.
I can't let you go any further.
I have no issues killing you a hundred times over!
target: Ez dut arazorik zu mila aldiz hiltzeko!

source: I suspect your immortality will be quite the problem.
target: Zure hilezkortasuna arazo izango dela susmatzen dut.

source: I will put an end to your quest for vengeance.
I won't be led into your trap.
I won't let you leave this place alive this time.
target: Oraingoan ez dizut hemendik bizirik joaten utziko.

source: I wouldn't have done that for you.
target: Zu banintz, ez nukeen horrelakorik egingo.

source: I'll be the one to take you down.
target: Ni izango naiz zurekin akabatuko duena.

source: I'll be with you in a moment.
I'll be with you in a moment.
I'll be with you in a moment.
I'll crush you all over again.
I'll destroy you and your selfish quest for vengeance!
target: Zu eta zure mendeku gose zeurekoia deuseztatuko zaituztet!

source: I'll go first... If you don't mind.
I'll make you pay for that!
I'm always looking to test my might.
target: Beti nago nire indarra probatzeko gogoz.

source: I'm getting tired of this shit!
I'm the one who's going to stop you.
I've longed for a battle like this.
target: Aspalditik nengoen horrelako borroka baten zain.

source: I've saved so many lives since taking your father's, but you won't accept that. You are blinded by vengeance!
target: Bizitza asko salbatu ditut zure aitarena hartu nuenetik, baina ez duzu onartu nahi. Mendekuak erabat itsuturik zauzka!

source: Interesting... Have you defeated death itself?
target: Interesgarria... Heriotza bera ere garaitu al duzu?

source: It's an honor to finally meet you.
It's an honor to have you here.
Lady Kuroki doesn't want to be disturbed.
target: Kuroki Andereak ez du inork eragozterik nahi.

source: Lady Kuroki doesn't want to be disturbed.
target: Kuroki Andereak ez du inork eragozterik nahi.

source: Let me end this fight now.
Let me get rid of that tension for you.
Life is hard, stressful... Please rest.
target: Bizitza gogorra eta estresagarria da... Mesedez, hartu atseden.

source: Look what we have. Only a fool would come here.
target: Begira zer dugun hemen. Ero bat bakarrik etorriko litzateke hona.

source: May I take you to your room, {ListenerGender}|gender(sir,madam)?
Nerves get the better of you?

target: Azken finean ez zara hain indartsua.

source: Now I understand how you were able to defeat the mute...
target: Orain ulertzen den dut nola menderatu ahal izan zenuen mutua...

source: Now, let's see how you handle my Pak Mei.
target: Ea nola daramazun nire Pak Mei-a.

source: Pathetic, you can barely keep up.
Pathetic. Have you forgotten how to hit someone?
target: Errukarria. Norbait nola jo behar den ahaztu duzu, ala?

source: Put that down before someone gets hurt.
target: Utzi ezazu hori norbaitek mina hartu baino lehen.

source: Ready to have your ass kicked?
Ready? Or do you need to catch your breath?
target: Prest? Edo hatsa berreskuratu behar duzu?

source: Sean imbued me with his strength.

target: Zu zara arazoak sortu dizkidana, beraz?
Zu zara arazoak sortu dizkidana, beraz?

source: Step by step, you inch closer to death.

target: Eman amore. Ezin duzu borrokan jarraitu.

source: That is the beginning of your end.
That one you get for free.
That was just the warm up.
target: Hori beroketa besterik ez da izan.

source: That won't work on me, fool.
target: Horrek nirekin ez du balio, ergela.

source: That's all you've got? After EIGHT years of training.
target: Hori al da dakizun guztia? ZORTZI urtez entrenatzen aritu eta gero.

source: The end is close for you now.
This is a dangerous game you're playing with me.
target: Joko arriskutsu batean ari zara nirekin jokatzen.

source: This is a fight you know you cannot win.
target: Badakizu borroka hau ezin duzula irabazi.

source: This is as far as you go.
target: Ez zara hau baino urrunago joango.

source: This is starting to bore me.
This is the part where I end you.
This is where I end you.
This is where I kill you.
This part of the club's off limits.
target: Klubeko eremu honek sarrera mugatua du.

source: This time my blades will not fail.
target: Oraingoan nire xaflek ez dute hutsik egingo.

source: Too late to back out now.
We're very pleased you chose the Sanctuary for your stay.
target: Ohorea da guretzat zuk Santutegian gelditzea erabaki izana.
Zergatik ez zara hiltzen, eta kito?
Zergatik ez zara hiltzen, eta kito?

source: Yang is waiting. Please follow me.
Yang requested that we take care of you.
You can run, but you can't hide.
target: Korri egin dezakezu, baina ezin zara gorde.

source: You can run, but you can't hide...
target: Korri egin dezakezu, baina ezin zara gorde...

source: You had such promise... Now look at you.
target: Etorkizun handia zenuen... begiratu orain zure buruari.

source: You look a little tense. I can fix that.
target: Urduri ikusten zaitut. Hori moldatu dezaket.

source: You look like you can fight. Show me.
target: Borroka egin dezakezula dirudi. Erakutsi iezadazu.

source: You look tired {ListenerGender}|gender(sir,madam), can I help you?
You look tired {ListenerGender}|gender(sir,madam), may I help you?
You lookin' to score or somethin'?
You must enjoy the taste of defeat.
You must enjoy the taste of defeat.
You never worked hard enough when you were young. I can see nothing has changed.
target: Gaztetan ez zinen inoiz nahikoa saiatzen. Ikusten dut ez zarela aldatu.

source: You should go back to training.
You should have stayed at home.
You shouldn't play these kinds of games with me.
target: Ez zenuke horrelako jokoetan nirekin aritu behar.

source: You will never escape this tower.
target: Ez duzu inoiz dorre honetatik ihes egingo.

source: You! I really don't like your face.
target: Zu! Ez zait zure aurpegia gustatzen.

source: You're a little too full of yourself.
You're in the right place if it's a fight you're after.
target: Leku egokian zaude borroka baldin bada nahi duzuna.

source: You're not as good as you think.
target: Ez zara uste duzuna bezain ona.

source: You're starting to annoy me... I wouldn't recommend it.
target: Zurekin nazkatzen hasia naiz... hori egitea ez da gomendagarria.

source: You've got determination, I'll give you that.
Your father didn't have time to teach you this.
target: Zure aitak ez zuen hau irakasteko denbora nahikorik izan.

source: Your father would have been proud.
Your presence disturbs the serenity of this place.
target: Zu egote hutsak leku honen lasaitasuna aztoratzen du.

source: Your reliance on your gift will be your downfall.
target: Zure dohainean duzun segurantza zure hondamena izango da.
